      "Keep your dog cool this summer with the Swamp Cooler Vest; It provides sun protection and evaporative cooling for hot weather activities such as hiking, walking, camping, and more",
      "We’ve updated the external air mesh for greater durability and water absorption; The new construction retains more water in high-exposure zones so they can play and explore more",
      "To activate, simply soak in water, wear and go; The outer layer reflects heat and facilitates evaporation while the updated middle layer absorbs more water to keep them cool longer",
      "Features an inner mesh lining keeps your pup dry and comfortable; The relaxed fit provides maximum shade with UPF 50+ to help protect them from the sun; Side-release buckles for easy on and off",
      "Wear on its own or layer over a harness with the integrated leash portal; Compatible with most harnesses, including Ruffwear’s Front Range, Hi & Light, and Web Master harnesses"
