          "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71PeUwd+xiL.jpg",
          "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/8187PjNsSXL.jpg"
        ],
        "is_verified_purchase": true
      },
      {
        "id": "R2RZSVCAKJL0SR",
        "asin": "R2RZSVCAKJL0SR",
        "title": "This product provides cooling comfort in serious heat!",
        "link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/customer-reviews/R2RZSVCAKJL0SR/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8",
        "text": "We are preparing for a life on the road with our dog so we bought this product to help keep him cool when we are in some hot climates. We are currently in Texas with temps in the 90s and Bueller is quite comfortable sitting outside. He did not object to putting it on and seems to forget that he is wearing it. Measurement guide was spot on for fit. Some of the features I like are the hidden and adjustable clips. Since the clips are hidden in the vest means I don’t have to worry about pinching him when I’m putting it on. I also like the leash attachment point at the top of it. The only suggestion I would offer is to embroider the words “cooling vest” on the sides so we stop getting dirty looks from people who think we are making our dog wear a sweater in the heat. Lol.",
        "rating": 5,
        "date": "Reviewed in the United States on June 12, 2022",
        "extracted_date": "2022-06-12",
        "profile": {
