        "helpful_votes": 27,
        "images": [
          "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81ZZ5e1l1YL.jpg"
        ],
        "is_verified_purchase": true
      },
      {
        "id": "R3JP26HSNQ979Q",
        "asin": "R3JP26HSNQ979Q",
        "title": "It works!",
        "link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/customer-reviews/R3JP26HSNQ979Q/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8",
        "text": "I purchased this mainly for my dog’s daily dog park trip. The temperature is still over 90 degree after 8pm here, and without the vest, my border collie doesn’t want to move after 15 mins. After putting on the vest, he can play his favorite high speed ball fetching game for an hour continuously, and his body under the vest still feels cool. However, the water will evaporate pretty quickly. A dripping vest will dry out after 50 mins exposed to heat, not sun. Simply pouring water on it won’t have the same effect as a dripping vest. if you plan to use this for a longer trip, make sure you have sufficient water source to keep it functioning.",
